@startuml
title The seev sub-domains and the custody chain
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor #F6E9F2
  BorderColor #A03C7A
}
skinparam package {
  BackgroundColor #FBF3F8
  BorderColor #A03C7A
}
skinparam ArrowColor #A03C7A

[Issuer] as ISS
[Issuer agent] as AG
[CSD] as CSD
[Custodian] as CUS
[Investor\n(account holder)] as INV

ISS --> AG : event terms
AG --> CSD : seev.009+ Agent CA messages
CSD --> CUS : seev.031 CA Notification\nseev.001 Meeting Notification
CUS --> INV : notify and collect elections
INV --> CUS : seev.033 CA Instruction / seev.004 Meeting Instruction
CUS --> CSD : forward elections and votes
@enduml
